path.id: For investors: Invest with a Purpose

As a potential investor, whilst gaining access to an alternative asset class with risk controlled systematic return, you can also join us on a mission to: Directly work with the artists for their next creative project, Gain portfolio exposure to music ventures and grow alongside the artist and be in the next chapter of their storytelling Enjoy a suite of live events, workshops and industry panels Empower social impact initiatives where music is used to address societal and humanitarian issues
